完美专业人士的自信。”</p><p>埃莉·古尔丁 (Ellie Goulding) 的帖子在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上首次出现<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ellie-goulding-assures-fans-her-face-is-intact-after-pyro-incident-3491163">后向粉丝保证，她的“脸完好无损”</a> 。</p> ;
